'''但河'''（[[希伯來語|希伯來語]]：דן dan，[[阿拉伯語|阿拉伯語]]：اللدان leddan），是[[中東|中東]]的一條河流，為[[約旦河|約旦河]]的支流。<ref>{{cite web|title=Dan River, Israel|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/150669/Dan-River|work=Encyclopædia Britannica|publisher=Encyclopædia Britannica Inc.|accessdate=8 March 2012|archive-date=2015-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150501062558/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/150669/Dan-River|dead-url=no}}</ref>河流水源來自{{link-en|但城 (古城)|Dan (ancient city)|但城}}一帶沿著地下斷層線冒出的多個水泉。<ref>{{cite journal | author = D. Gil'ad and J. Bonne | title = The Snowmelt of Mt. Hermon and its Contribution to the Sources of the Jordan River | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-hydrology_1990-03_114_1-2/page/n8 | journal  = Journal of Hydrology | volume = 114 | year = 1990 | pages = 1–15 | doi=10.1016/0022-1694(90)90072-6}}</ref>

河名源自古代[[迦南|以色列人]]城市「但城」，在《[[士師記|士師記]]》時期由[[但支派|但支派]]佔領。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Biran|first=Avram|title=Tel Dan|journal=The Biblical Archaeologist|date=May 1974|volume=37|issue=2|pages=26–51|jstor=3210948|publisher=The American Schools of Oriental Research}}</ref>雖然但河本身只有20公里長，它每年供應多達238百萬立方公尺的水給{{link-en|胡拉河谷|Hulah Valley}}。

